        </div>
        <div class="list">
            <div class="subdiv"> 
                <h3>Practice work List:</h3>
                <a href="/userDetails/dynamictable">1. Dynamic Table</a>
                <a href="/userDetails/kukucube">2. KuKu Cube</a>
